divs: Sighting Detailsout walking my dog on street below my house, my husband noticed lights going over house. The two objects were showing identical light patterns to the last sighting. Both were heading in same flight path as the first three. I am not sure if it were the same craft or different ones from same group,The ojects were silent and moving really fast.
